name: Cherry Pie with Heart and Star Cutouts - Miniature Pendant / Charm
description:
Freshly baked cherry pie with star and heart patterned cut-outs so you can see the cherries! Completely handmade and baked in stages to ensure that it is perfect, realistic and durable.

This pie has a loop and bail made out of silver enamelled copper wire that does not contain any nickel or lead. The silver will not tarnish. The pie is 2.5cm in diameter, and hangs about 3cm together with the bail.

This listing is for the pie pendant only.

Your pie will be baked to order, so please allow up to 7 days for me to complete and ship it out. :D
You can also request a different metal colour. I have gold enamelled, rose gold enamelled, and pure solid copper.

name: Caramel Cream Tarts w/ Fruits - Miniature Food Earrings and Jewelry
description:
Sweet miniature polymer clay tarts with caramel cream, banana and strawberry slices!

These are attached to gold enamelled ear wires (no nickel or lead), hand forged by me. Other coloured metals are available, including silver enamelled, rose gold enamelled, stainless steel and solid copper.

These are M-sized tarts. Each tart is about 1.8cm x 1.3cm, but may vary a little due to being handmade. Combined with ear wires, the total hanging length is about 4cm.

Your pair of tart earrings will be baked especially for you. You may also order these in different coloured cream or fruit slices. Since I will make these as orders come in, please allow 5-7 business days for me to make and ship them out.

name: Red Heart Donuts - Stainless Steel Earrings - Miniature Food Jewelry
description:
Chocolate icing donuts with red candy hearts on them! I'm sure this will be a delight for heart silhouette and donut lovers. Also perfect for a special someone, and on valentine's day.

Donuts are attached to stainless steel stud posts. Hypo-allergenic and great for sensitive skin. Each donut is about 0.9cm in diameter.

These will be handmade for you. Let me know if you would like to customise the colours (no charge). Please allow up to 5 business days for me to complete and ship them out. Thanks for looking!
